<h1>iMac 27" 2015: Display Backlight Failure</h1>

<div class="case-meta">
  <span class="case-date">April 2024</span>
  <span class="case-device">iMac 27-inch Late 2015 (A1419)</span>
  <span class="case-category">Display Repair</span>
